<h3>NetHack Poll 2009</h3>

The poll was opened in november 2009 and close in february 2010.

The results of this poll can be downloaded <a href="nethack_poll_results.txt">here in text form</a>.

The intention of this poll is to gather some information about NetHack players, both currently active and past players for helping us variants developers for design decisions and to get a small insight into the NetHack community as a whole.

Even if you no longer play NetHack regularly, please take part in this poll. Most questions make sense also for former players and one question asks explicitly why you no longer play NetHack.

Please spread the word about this poll to other NetHack playing people you know.

Instead of filling out this form you can also send us an e-mail to <a href="mailto:nethackpoll@gmail.com?subject=NetHack Poll 2009: ">nethackpoll@gmail.com</a>. The questions can also be downloaded as a <a href="nethack_poll.txt">text file</a>.

